posting_body: ['Uniquely Bright & Newly Rehabbed 2bed/1bath', 'Property Address', '2721 W Division St - 3R | Chicago, IL 60622', 'Available:', '09/01/2022', 'Offered By', 'Campbell Street Asset Management Inc', 'Description', 'Gorgeous 2 bed with high ceilings, spacious closets!', 'All new washer dryer in unit, SS stove, fridge and dishwasher, Granite counter tops, with white cabinetry.', 'Everything is new from floor to ceiling.', 'With sundrenched Luxury finishes throughout, you can truly Live Comfortable.', 'Conveniently located near CTA bus routes and close to 90/94.', 'Experience the culture of Humboldt Parks restaurants, bars, shops, bodegas, barbers and the historic Humboldt Park Field House and grounds.', 'Humboldt Park and Field House boast, lagoons, tennis courts, baseball diamonds small beaches, lagoons, bike trails and tons of green grass space for summer picnics and play.', '$55 application fee', 'Move in fees:', '$350 if one person', '$250/person', 'if more than one person', '$200/pet + $30/month rent', 'Please reach out to Mercedes at 31two.68two.0306 for faster response.', 'Photos are representative of unit.', 'Details', 'Beds/Baths: 2BD/1.0BA', 'Square Feet: 650', 'Rental Terms', 'Rent: $1,645.00', 'Available:', '09/01/2022', 'Application Fee: $55.00', 'Pet Policy', 'Cats allowed', 'Dogs allowed']
